faq.question: How can I track my order?
faq.answer: You can track your order using the “Track Order” option in your account dashboard.

faq.question: What payment methods do you accept?
faq.answer: We accept credit/debit cards, UPI, net banking, and wallet payments.

faq.question: Is Cash on Delivery available?
faq.answer: Yes, Cash on Delivery is available on select products and locations.

faq.question: How do I return a product?
faq.answer: Go to “My Orders,” select the item, and click on “Return.” Follow the instructions provided

faq.question: What is the warranty period for products?
faq.answer: Warranty varies by product. You can find warranty details on the product page

faq.question: Can I cancel my order after placing it?
faq.answer: Yes, you can cancel your order before it is shipped. Visit “My Orders” to cancel

faq.question: How do I contact customer support?
faq.answer: You can reach us via live chat, email, or call our helpline available 24/7.
